=Description=

"In the aftermath of Chernobyl, a handful of committed citizens decided to become active together in their community in the Black Forest and create a nuclear- and coal-free energy supply belonging to citizens. Today the EWS supplies people throughout Germany with green power and eco-gas and works in various ways towards bringing about the energy revolution. Discover more about the extraordinary story of Schönau's electricity rebels!"
(https://www.ews-schoenau.de/ews/international/)

